refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
&style.oop;
static array Locale::parseLocale stringlocale
&style.procedural;
array locale_parse stringlocale
Returns a key-value array of locale ID subtag elements.

&reftitle.parameters;
locale
The locale to extract the subtag array from. Note: The 'variant' and 'private' subtags can take maximum 15 values whereas 'extlang' can take maximum 3 values.

  &reftitle.examples;

   locale_parse example


<?php
$arr = locale_parse('sl-Latn-IT-nedis');
if ($arr) {
    foreach ($arr as $key => $value) {
        echo "$key : $value , ";
    }
}
?>




   OO example


<?php
$arr = Locale::parseLocale('sl-Latn-IT-nedis');
if ($arr) {
    foreach ($arr as $key => $value) {
        echo "$key : $value , ";
    }
}
?>



  &example.outputs;


language : sl , script : Latn , region : IT , variant0 : NEDIS ,
